---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Cybrid Lab" description="About Leo and Cybrid Lab — where tech meets life.">
  <article class="prose space-y-6">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      I'm Leo. I build things at the intersection of finance, tech, and AI,
      and I write about what I find there.
    </p>
    <p>
      Cybrid Lab is part notebook, part playground — a place for technical
      write-ups, project notes, and the occasional personal reflection. If
      you're drawn to the frontier of how these fields are reshaping each
      other, you're in the right place.
    </p>

    <h2>What is "Cybrid"?</h2>
    <p>
      A blend of <strong>cyber</strong> and <strong>hybrid</strong> — a lab for
      minds that don't fit neatly into one box.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>
      Find me on <a href="https://github.com/leoyoung-69" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      or subscribe to the <a href="/rss.xml">RSS feed</a> to stay updated.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
